{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":130,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563883912/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=7\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563883912/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":10},"data":[{"id":568473324,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568473324","content":"问题不是尖子生和差生，不是水平的问题。问题是他学习态度不端正，走了邪路。他做题之前不去学习具体的解题需要的知识，也没有去看尖子生们之前做错的思路。研究的过程里前置知识的掌握可以说是必须的，他没有去学。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e巨人的肩膀他都爬不上去，何况巨人也才辛苦爬在半山腰，他就站在山脚叫着山脚有电梯能登顶。这是典型的想要科学研究的成果和名利，不愿意吃科学研究的苦头。\u003cbr\u003e“尖子生”们老老实实吃苦头攀爬科学高峰为后来者开路，更多的“差生”们，还没有掌握这么多知识的高中生们也老老实实吃苦头，从头爬起“尖子生”们为他们开的路，爬到和尖子生平齐，也就是尖子生了。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e这一个“差生”不想着先老老实实学习爬山，就号称看到山顶大家没看过的风景，比所有人爬得都高，这就是在侮辱所有认真爬山相信付出才有回报的人的汗水，大家的批评和嘲讽是看不惯这种妄想不劳而获的学习态度。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546309070,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":9,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":48,"child_comments":[{"id":568487138,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568487138","content":"所以正确的做法是指出错误指明学习方向而不是嘲讽。现在的情况是，没人知道到底该往那条路走，初等方法依然没有被证明不可行，试图用初等方法最多是自不量力，事实上，人类的进步总需要这种“自不量力”的精神，只要能够虚心学习这种精神就能成为前进的动力。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546311215,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":1,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":568493331,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568493331","content":"在开始的几十个回答里，大多数劝他好好学习，考上大学再说，还是很温和的。因为他的问题(知乎规定回答要切题)，大家觉得他功利心太重，嘲讽也是有的。还有的数学话题优秀答主一类的希望题主先把证明发给自己看一看，避免有太明显的低级错误到时候伤到他。这都是很善意的劝诫了。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e可是他呢，统一留言1.1知乎发表证明哥德巴赫猜想，不愿意给任何一个数学专业的答主看一看，对自己的“证明”无比自信。问题提的有目的性(上清北)显得研究动机非常功利(也暴露了无知)，又发表文章说“也不需要多高深的数学知识”，想要打脸全世界，把整个数学界的脸放在地上踩。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e大家才开始嘲讽和打压的，这孩子走了邪路了。不打压说些“鼓励”！“加油”！“有勇气！”之类的话难道不是纵容他越走越歪吗？实打实告诉他你水平不行，你证不出来，再学个五六七八年才有水平研究这类问题之类的。让他别这么盲目地傲气好好准备高考，我觉得没什么错，也是他先种下的因。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546312146,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":4,"reply_to_author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0}]}]}
